Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自小就喜欢缤纷小鸟的画册
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞往不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环绕不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终颜色凝固在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缤纷小鸟渐渐死去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分悲惨的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  为何我会这么向往缤纷小鸟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没法触及那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法触及Gold  Saw
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为Gold  Saw依然被困在她的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Rock  Shooter里的真透
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对沙耶的呼唤有反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  万一你去了那边的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于我们的她就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我不去的话  真透就无法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透是个不可思议的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨  嫉妒  烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很少会有这种感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说  她很痛恨烦恼本身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛恨烦恼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她否定烦恼的自己  想帮助烦恼的他人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种心情  形成了Black  Rock  Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了帮某人解脱烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也要抹杀掉某人的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Rock  Shooter一定会把属于我们的她打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就再也无法呼唤真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么好像前提就是要她消失一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这个意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和真透两人都不会消失  我不会让她们消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来承蒙你照顾了  沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒来  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音  是优吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  我不会原谅你伤害她的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要继续互相伤害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要输  你要尽力想着脱离那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:07:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  想着脱离Black  Rock  Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大喊出来  这个人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Rock  Shooter不是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  老是傻乎乎的  经常丢三落四
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  虽说是自己的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实话说  是个挺好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  看起来像个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像没什么存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  虽然性格开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不愿意打开心扉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会说漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲经常出差  我还担心她会感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她从来没有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点觉得她太成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负面的话一句也不说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乖了  反而让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是给她的压力太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  真透  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没有伤心事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家其实都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能够相互理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直  都希望能这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌犹豫不决地烦恼着的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌会有憎恨他人之心的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是不想伤害自己的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想自己被人嫌弃的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自小就喜欢缤纷小鸟的画册
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后染成一片漆黑的缤纷小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过  向往着肮脏的缤纷小鸟罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的缤纷小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  Black  Rock  Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想受伤  这有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有错  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透你想错了  你没有逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好地面对现实解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避的不是真透
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避的不是真透  是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌说我坏话的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老这么叽叽喳喳吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  很痛啊  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优  这孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放着我不管吧  会救我的吧  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我们这样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要向我提意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有义务要保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧  Strength！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼也未免太迟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣真透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好像至今我的Strength都受你关照一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Strength…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是神足优
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在Strength和你一样在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好像有什么非常痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就是想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎想不起来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有人看到黑衣同学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同学今天不是休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才接到她家里的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是从昨天起就没回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？离家出走？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是被绑架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静  安静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黄泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了初中生  成为了同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅如此…但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察啊  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个地方好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我也会去找的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  那么重要的时候却请假
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优居然是Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优的心里有着深刻的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这个世界中战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实世界中少女们的痛苦和烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育了这个世界和我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来没有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是遵从少女们的感情  依靠本能战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的世界里  Black  Rock  Shooter出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到她非常强大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只会战斗的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负和我毫无相关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是在死亡前的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了优的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬间我拥有了感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优的痛苦是别的少女无法比拟的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有巨大的质量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是这样的质量影响了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次产生感情的我  不禁这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优的感情基本都是由痛苦和憎恶构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我抱着全部感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Black  Rock  Shooter杀了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优还会剩下什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有死太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你死了  我可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我消失的话  你的烦恼也会消…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的世界很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是些残酷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:19:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是些痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你现在抱着我的烦恼死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又会产生新的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那时你不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此相比  这边的世界简单多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛是最显而易见的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  和我换一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互换？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  互换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会留在这个世界里的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现实里由你来承受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你背负这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是求你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我保护那个世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  只有那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能成为她的保护伞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想思考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  明明好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字起得好聪明！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…去看五彩缤纷的万物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去就和小鸟游同学一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黄泉一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会想要忘记真透呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！
